nology</strong>&nbsp;is a high-end system with server-class performance in a 6-bay desktop form factor. It features dual M.2 2280 NVMe SSD cache slots, a 10 Gigabit Ethernet port, and a scalable storage design, all of which allow you to boost the performance of your NAS. It is also equipped with a PCIe 3.0 x8/x8 slot for system expansion, as well as six drive bays that are capable of natively supporting 3.5" SATA hard drives, as well as 2.5" SATA hard drives and SSDs. Using its six drive bays, this NAS will allow you to store and share a large number of files, including videos, music, photos, and documents with up to 16,000 user accounts and 8000 maximum concurrent connections.</p>
