<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<h5 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><span style="font-size: 18pt; background-color: rgb(251, 238, 184);">何謂PrismX&trade;網路控制器？</span></h5>
</div>
</div>
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-141a8ab elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="141a8ab" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
<p>PrismX&trade;網路控制器是專為企業級Wi-Fi網路需求所設計的中央管理資訊主頁。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><img src="https://hi5-brtech-ecommerce.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/images/l-d25bd8a8-086c-46e2-bf5f-881aa231fdd8.jpg"></p>
