<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<h5 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><span style="font-size: 18pt; background-color: rgb(251, 238, 184);">如何理想佈建PrismX&trade;網路控制器？</span></h5>
</div>
</div>
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8a4c393 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8a4c393" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
<p>PrismX&trade;網路控制器可以佈建於現場 桌上型電腦、Mac電腦或Linux設備上；亦可以在私有雲或公共雲上使用服務。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><img src="https://hi5-brtech-ecommerce.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/images/l-684621a5-85a7-4fe0-ad4e-830f8f85caec.jpg"></p>
