<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''新細明體'',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 新細明體;">量身打造的<span lang="EN-US"> Galaxy</span></span></strong></p>
