<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''新細明體'',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 新細明體;">換上大地色彩</span></strong></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;">採用稍微特別一點的設計。全新色彩的靈感來自大自然，轉化成天然染料，注入富有光澤的金屬框架。<span lang="EN-US">&sup1; &sup2;</span></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''新細明體'',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 新細明體;">夜，更顯明亮</span></strong></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;">拍出人人欣羨的精彩夜拍照片。超明亮夜幕攝影透過增強<span lang="EN-US"> AI </span>確保細節清楚分明，從黃昏到黎明的低光源時段，拍攝的照片和影片仍舊明亮鮮豔。</p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''新細明體'',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 新細明體;">細節，無所遁形</span></strong></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US">5000</span>萬畫素廣角鏡頭與強大晶片相輔相成，迅速結合不同畫格，從中擷取細節，整合成單一高解析度照片。新增清晰度增強器技術，呈現清晰無比的畫質，禁得起一再放大影像。</p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''新細明體'',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 新細明體;">給你更多力量</span></strong></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;">世上最快的<span lang="EN-US"> Snapdragon&sup3; </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',serif;">⁴</span><span lang="EN-US"><br></span>如果不想遭遇運行中斷，這個革新的晶片可提高手機的遊戲和影片串流效能，而且電池續航力更長，讓你整天都不需要擔心手機沒電。</p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''新細明體'',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 新細明體;">大幅延長玩遊戲的時間</span></strong></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US">Galaxy S23 </span>和<span lang="EN-US"> S23+ </span>的電池續航力更長，分別為<span lang="EN-US"> 3900mAh (</span>典型值<span lang="EN-US">) </span>和<span lang="EN-US"> 4700mAh (</span>典型值<span lang="EN-US">)</span><span style="font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic'';">⁵</span>，充電速度更快，方便你長時間玩遊戲和追劇。</p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''新細明體'',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 新細明體;">眩光不再</span></strong></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;">在任何光線下，自動調節螢幕亮度，呈現最佳色彩，到處都能玩遊戲或串流。<span style="font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic'';">⁶</span><span lang="EN-US"> 120Hz </span>螢幕更新率，提供順暢的捲動操作，並且藉由舒適護眼模式，即使在黑暗中看螢幕，眼睛也不會覺得疲勞。</p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: ''新細明體'',serif; mso-bidi-font-family: 新細明體;">量身打造的<span lang="EN-US"> Galaxy</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;">設定專屬於你的手機介面，現在前所未有地簡單。<span lang="EN-US">One UI </span>提供最齊全的自訂功能，從鎖定螢幕和介面主題，到小工具和通知功能，都能客製化。</p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt;">&sup1;</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt;">販售顏色可能因國家<span lang="EN-US">/</span>地區或經銷商而異。<span lang="EN-US"><br>&sup2;</span>金屬框架的陽極處理染料是以<span lang="EN-US">10%</span>天然染料製成。<span lang="EN-US"><br>&sup3;</span>根據<span lang="EN-US"> Qualcomm Technologies, Inc. </span>進行的規格和產業效能評測，截至<span lang="EN-US">2023</span>年<span lang="EN-US">4</span>月<span lang="EN-US">30</span>日，僅<span lang="EN-US"> Galaxy S23 </span>系列獨有。<span lang="EN-US"><br></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',serif;">⁴</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt;">Snapdragon </span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt;">是<span lang="EN-US"> QualcommTechnologies, Inc. </span>和<span lang="EN-US">/</span>或其子公司的產品。<span lang="EN-US">Snapdragon </span>是<span lang="EN-US"> Qualcomm Incorporated </span>的商標或註冊商標。</span></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="hubble-uspitem" style="margin-left: 36pt; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic'';">⁵</span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt;">在第三方實驗室環境下測試的典型值。典型值是考慮到<span lang="EN-US"> IEC 61960 </span>標準測試的電池樣品中電池容量偏差的估計平均值。<span lang="EN-US">Galaxy S23 </span>的額定容量為<span lang="EN-US"> 3785mAh</span>、<span lang="EN-US">Galaxy S23+ </span>為<span lang="EN-US"> 4565mAh</span>、<span lang="EN-US">Galaxy S23 Ultra </span>為<span lang="EN-US"> 4855mAh</span>。實際電池壽命可能根據網路環境、使用模式和其他因素而不同。<span lang="EN-US"><br></span></span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: ''MS Gothic''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''MS Gothic'';">⁶</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.0pt;">Galaxy S23 </span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt;">和<span lang="EN-US"> S23+ </span>的<span lang="EN-US"> Dynamic AMOLED 2X </span>顯示螢幕榮獲德國<span lang="EN-US"> VDE </span>認證，擁有視覺增強功能，能夠在<span lang="EN-US"> DCI-P3 </span>顏色範圍實現<span lang="EN-US">100%</span>的移動色域，意即圖像不會褪色，不論亮度如何，都能精彩呈現豐富飽滿的色彩畫面。顯示螢幕的峰值亮度可達<span lang="EN-US">1750 nits</span>，改善數位影像的明暗對比，讓畫質更亮麗，<span lang="EN-US">3,000,000:1 </span>的對比度則讓你的行動體驗更具臨場感。</span></p>
